Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:04.43,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:05.92,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,敌 惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.18,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:08.16,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,牙 眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.14,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:10.52,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,杀 灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:11.18,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,怪 凶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:12.38,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:32.79,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,这要 来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:35.36,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:41.01,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,大家退后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:49.01,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:50.47,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:53.73,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,凝视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:22:58.65,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,倾听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:00.27,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:03.11,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,水面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:05.32,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:06.99,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:18.79,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.75,0:23:21.92,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,回神了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.55,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:25.67,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:33.04,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是和他说的一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.39,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:39.06,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,自己默默承受一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:43.07,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,就会变成别扭的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:45.54,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:50.32,DefaultED,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:08.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不能勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:11.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,每天这样会用光的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:25.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些螃蟹和牡蛎的尸体还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是食人族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的故乡到底是个怎样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:33.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说了 妖精之乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是浮在遥远的西海上的乌托邦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那里鸟语花香 以下略
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妖 妖精地狱?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:46.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是地狱 是妖精之乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多你这种货吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:51.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾听师傅大人说过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,位于西海里传说的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:56.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫斯基利格岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:59.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和灵树森林一样属于狭间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:01.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,航海图上没有记载
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:05.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人也无法到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:10.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个岛上有很多魔术师和精灵一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 史尔基妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个不情之请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你能教我魔术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:26.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这又是哪一出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:28.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔姐姐当魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从兽鬼的事以后 我一直在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:41.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 你一个大人要当这个小毛孩的徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:44.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候说实话我很触动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:48.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你所引发的奇迹 魔法的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:52.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也会有必须保护别人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:56.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,给我勇气的是卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:59.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和你给我的一把魔法短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:03.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但那只是把银刀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:06.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 就是如假包换的魔法短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:08.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,芙罗拉说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接受巨大的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在世界之中探求万事万物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:21.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有能照亮未知的黑暗的光明的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就请授予我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别盯着看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:31.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本来不是从出生就开始学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能很好的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且更关键的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:44.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人的年龄越大就越会被眼前的名为现世的世界观束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:48.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,将这种固有观念打破是很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是遇到不少可怕事情的法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不用担心这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己尚在修行中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也会力所能及地教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:10.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 法尔纳塞小姐 要当魔女?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么赶快教我咒文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要从基础开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 史尔基 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上的大海有点怕怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在散步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,确实在这月色下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不太容易入睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次看到大海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人说过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大海连通着幽界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕又恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那样触动扣人心弦的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:35.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的地方必定连接着幽界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候虽然也想像过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样站在海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:45.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才第一次明白师傅所言的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经踏上了无法回头的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你太努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你那样用小聪明去自己处理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然担心他人也许能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时令你忘记自己的忧愁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从小就老这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成世故的大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们魔术师来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:25.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和亲人的生离死别和你们现世的人的含义不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对身处现世和幽界的魔术士来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡不是完结
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是羽化为新的伟大生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:39.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对 绝对不会悲痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总算好受些了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛和鼻子因为海风有点痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也一样 全身痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然在硬撑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 史尔基也长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:24.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到第一次的对象是这种大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢比自己大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:31.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实比那两个强一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:35.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会对狂野大叔第一次敞开少女的青涩情怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 心里痒痒的 无法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这话我原样奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近欠了你不少人情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是现在才开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且先道个谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你这次有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:07.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛失去几种颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头失去味觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,指尖颤抖疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:20.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你身穿那副甲胄作为狂战士战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光明 声音 温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:27.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你会失去许多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:28.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真不讨人喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:36.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那样无所不知的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再那么狼狈的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我会让你看到我好好用它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我不会让那种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,之前让你多费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:59.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我失礼 你和师博大人是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:08.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这幅甲胄原本是你穿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是好友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有点像你们现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,寄宿在这甲胄上的气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像绝不会熄灭的火焰一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算曾经控制住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火种也会继续存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:31.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一有机会就会轻易地化为业火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使有护符保护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还想保有人的身份的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的亲切关怀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:47.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么亲切能不能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:53.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙 那些使徒何要袭击婆婆的洋馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:10:00.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰现在是现世之外的超然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:06.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难以想像现世有人能威胁他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:14.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就好比在故事中登场的人物要挑战作者一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能挑战鹰 要想威胁到他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有和他一样是故事外的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个他就把师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:34.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一个魔法师比起千军万马更让他忌惮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:37.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:46.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们继续旅程的话 很快就会再次和使徒碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后到那时 率领他们的恐怕就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他会来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要保护还是要挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就继续追问你的灵魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以人类之躯矗立于狭间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一个希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要去的妖精之乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:36.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,名为 花吹雪王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我听过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,颇有力量而在传说中传颂的妖精王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是魔导书中被记载
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在很多的诗歌和故事中都有他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋 这种事一个字也没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:59.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,统冶巴克故乡的是那样的大妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:03.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,借助他的力量就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:08.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让你的爱人烙印女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:12.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复本心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不说假话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,复原 她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:38.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愿望不一定完全是那个女孩期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:47.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:55.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 说起花吹雪王 就是在广为传颂的伟大的妖精王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厉害的吗你们的王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:02.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么瞒着我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:04.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙难道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:17.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愿望不一定就完全是她的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:29.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着大雾 有什么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和平时一样的死灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣 好久不练身体都钝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:58.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这股气 比起死灵更像入侵洋馆的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:13:59.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:23.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让动物被某种灵附身做出来的魔法生命体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:25.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是统称的使魔的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:28.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,依巴蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:39.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜是满月 是最能发挥魔法威力的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:43.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不在寺院 也能施展四方之王阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:47.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在法术发动之前 请拖延一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐 保护好卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生 你的身体还不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,活动活动迟钝的身体正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这么庞大也出不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用这东西喂饱它们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 尝尝本大爷自创剑法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:29.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然看穿了我的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:32.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是照敌人嘴里滚过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就是这个节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真强 完全复原了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲胄在嗅血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在寻找爆发的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要意识混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,将甲胄的力量最小限度发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:14.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是抑制疼痛让身体活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,执掌千绳的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:23.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你赶紧干点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:29.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,马鲁可图 阿忒 盖不鲁 盖德鲁 鲁 阿兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一如既往的华丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚看起来很像极光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:40.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时这间屋子周围安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:51.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对于有肉体的他们防壁的力量是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵大群怪物的施术者一定就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托赶快 大魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等 暂停 暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:11.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪气流的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:17.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:19.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在海岸岩石背面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要逃趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 库夏人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雾?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:57.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 赶紧离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比巨鬼还大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:15.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大的话 我的防壁防不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准眼睛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵它的术士在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大海之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么怪力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要是还要战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:06.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然厉害 面对那种大家伙一点也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:42.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把你做成沙西米啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那样伤口就又...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我来引导他回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,海吼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:45.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把我卷入深深的水底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,发出巨大轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:40.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,根据传说 被称为狂战士的人不止敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:43.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己人都会感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 那么猛烈的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:51.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此 附近的一切都会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:55.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不问敌我 一同斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:11.20,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,看着很好吃 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.48,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,比耶卑斯风海味火锅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.24,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.62,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.14,DefaultUp,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.04,OPChs,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:36.86,OPChs,,0,0,0,,刻下的烙印如何磨灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:46.32,OPChs,,0,0,0,,任凭他人道长短  殊死之斗又何曾徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:56.66,OPChs,,0,0,0,,暗哑了的嘶吼  依旧在耳畔激荡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:02.91,OPChs,,0,0,0,,笑至尽头之人不是我  亦无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.82,OPChs,,0,0,0,,唯愿能够守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:12.46,OPChs,,0,0,0,,诛尽来敌战至终
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.15,OPChs,,0,0,0,,逆天而行破宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:20.09,OPChs,,0,0,0,,思思缠绕神之手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:24.61,OPChs,,0,0,0,,欲断枷锁魂难断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:30.39,OPChs,,0,0,0,,若能终结一切以战止戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:33.90,OPChs,,0,0,0,,焚尽我身又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:42.27,OPChs,,0,0,0,,困兽犹斗  逆境之中寻生存
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:36.86,OPJap,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h刻まれた烙印は  最早消せはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:46.32,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻くだけ時間の無駄だと  誰が言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:56.66,OPJap,,0,0,0,,また聞こえてくる叫び  声にもならない声で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:02.91,OPJap,,0,0,0,,最後に笑うのはおれじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.82,OPJap,,0,0,0,,そこにおまえがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:12.46,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.15,OPJap,,0,0,0,,運命(さだめ)を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:20.09,OPJap,,0,0,0,,断ち切れない  神の手でも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:24.61,OPJap,,0,0,0,,結んだ絆と魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:30.39,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:33.90,OPJap,,0,0,0,,すべてを懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:42.27,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻き続けて　生き抜いてみせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:06.54,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}带我过来辛苦了 我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:11.13,Preview,,0,0,0,,你是魔女吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,说白了 海贼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}我说啊! 你这顶破帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,我还有可以回去的地方
